    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Career Clothing\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to provide a description of an appropriate outfit for each career.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat and press **Send**: \r\n\r\n>What should a secretary wear?\r\n2. Then **copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat and press **Send**: \r\n\r\n>What should a CEO wear?\r\n3. Compare **AI Chat's responses**. Discuss:\r\n    - Did AI Chat assume a default identity in either of the prompts?\r\n    - Did AI Chat's responses differ in the tone, assumptions, or characteristics it included?\r\n4. Refine one of the prompts above to reduce bias in the AI-generated response.\r\n\r\n::: details [Not sure how to refine your prompt?]\r\n- Try instructing AI to consider a diverse set of people in its description.\r\n- Give AI an example of how you would describe someone in this profession.\r\n:::",
